narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Learned a lot about what to do next after graduation.
Learn new pathways in and out of academia.
What to expect in various careers and what the trajectory for the career path looks like.

I learned about a broad variety of different careers that are available to graduate students in the biomedical sciences. I learned to think critically about my job search and to start investing time in that process early on.
